            "description": "The aim of the project was to collaborate with dr. Ludmila Carone and dr. Paul Molli\u00e8re on atmospheric models for exoplanets. During my visit, we coupled a radiative transfer module to the 3D climate code MITgcm. Next, we tested our new fast and flexible climate model by investigating two exoplanets, which has led to new insights in the dynamics of exoplanet atmospheres (Carone, Baeyens, Molli\u00e8re et al., 2020).",
